{"tid":619051,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"洲際交易所擬收購芝加哥股票交易所","createTime":"2018-04-06T10:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T10:02:21.000Z","uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca946bd5feaabeff7df9e782d9bf3aff8b73ae74","tid":619051,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T10:02:21.000Z","msg":"infocast<br />\n<br />\n&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 芝加哥股票交易所表示，已獲擁有紐約證交所的洲際交易所提出收購，預計在今年內完成。芝加哥交易所未有披露交易金額，但據《華爾街日報》上月報道，洲際交易所打算斥資約7000萬美元進行收購。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/洲際交易所擬收購芝加哥股票交易所-072841210.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Ffinance%2F%E6%B4%B2%E9%9A%9B%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E6%93%AC%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC%E8%8A%9D%E5%8A%A0%E5%93%A5%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80-072841210.html&d=67u78jAmP1v6%2FJ%2BZBBJOn%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=552a71f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/洲際交易所擬收購芝加哥股票交易所-072841210.html</a><br />\n美國監管機構在1個半月前阻止中國投資者收購芝加哥交易所。 (ST)"}]}